1
00:01:35,900 --> 00:01:40,980
=Love Beyond the Grave=
(Halaw mula sa nobela ni Li Qingran)

2
00:01:41,260 --> 00:01:43,990
=Episode 25=

3
00:02:28,070 --> 00:02:29,630
Yan Zhang, ikaw iyon.

4
00:03:43,620 --> 00:03:44,460
Sa totoo lang,

5
00:03:47,270 --> 00:03:49,230
Hindi ko kailanman sasabihin.

6
00:04:17,030 --> 00:04:18,470
Isang araw,

7
00:04:20,230 --> 00:04:21,070
Yan Ke,

8
00:04:24,230 --> 00:04:25,790
mamamatay ka rin

9
00:04:27,260 --> 00:04:28,940
sa kamay ng taong mahal mo.

10
00:04:46,150 --> 00:04:47,110
Bai Sanxing.

11
00:04:52,590 --> 00:04:53,430
Bai Sanxing.

12
00:05:14,420 --> 00:05:15,710
Sinabi ko bang patayin mo siya?

13
00:05:16,910 --> 00:05:17,910
Hindi sa iyo si Bai Sanxing

14
00:05:17,910 --> 00:05:18,750
harapin.

15
00:05:40,990 --> 00:05:42,910
Yan Zhang, Vice Lord ng Xuling Temple,

16
00:05:43,260 --> 00:05:45,180
mga sinaktan na espiritu at mga huwad na papet,

17
00:05:45,380 --> 00:05:46,420
nagdudulot ng kapahamakan sa walang bisa,

18
00:05:46,790 --> 00:05:48,550
at lumabag sa Bilangguan,

19
00:05:49,150 --> 00:05:50,820
nakikipagsabwatan sa felon na si Bai Sanxing

20
00:05:50,820 --> 00:05:51,873
upang magplano laban sa Kanyang Grasya.

21
00:05:52,230 --> 00:05:53,070
Pagkatapos ng imbestigasyon,

22
00:05:53,420 --> 00:05:54,670
conclusive ang ebidensya.

23
00:05:56,150 --> 00:05:57,710
Ang punong salarin, si Yan Zhang,

24
00:05:58,420 --> 00:06:00,380
ay nilipol ng Kanyang Grasya.

25
00:06:00,820 --> 00:06:03,500
Nahuli na rin si Bai Sanxing.

26
00:06:04,300 --> 00:06:05,140
Mula sa araw na ito,

27
00:06:05,550 --> 00:06:07,030
hanapin ang lahat ng Void,

28
00:06:07,620 --> 00:06:08,940
at tugisin ang mga kasabwat ni Yan.

29
00:06:09,300 --> 00:06:11,500
Punasan ang natitirang mga puppet

30
00:06:11,500 --> 00:06:12,500
sa lalong madaling panahon.

31
00:06:13,180 --> 00:06:15,150
Sinumang mga espiritu na nag-uudyok ng gulo

32
00:06:15,820 --> 00:06:17,260
dapat ding parusahan ng batas.

33
00:06:19,180 --> 00:06:20,940
Oo, Your Grace.

34
00:06:22,180 --> 00:06:23,020
Your Grace,

35
00:06:23,150 --> 00:06:24,790
paano mo haharapin si Bai Sanxing?

36
00:06:25,260 --> 00:06:26,420
Napalunok siya ng napakaraming kapatid

37
00:06:26,570 --> 00:06:27,420
sa aking templo.

38
00:06:27,420 --> 00:06:28,830
Dapat siyang mamatay para dito.

39
00:06:35,710 --> 00:06:37,060
May plano ang kanyang Grace.

40
00:06:37,710 --> 00:06:38,550
Ngunit...

41
00:06:43,990 --> 00:06:44,940
Kung wala nang iba,

42
00:06:44,940 --> 00:06:45,940
maaari kang umalis sa ngayon.

43
00:06:47,260 --> 00:06:48,100
Oo.

44
00:06:52,990 --> 00:06:54,550
Sige na, sige na. Ilipat.

45
00:06:56,180 --> 00:06:58,060
Sino ang nakakaalam na si Yan Zhang ay napakalupit?

46
00:06:58,060 --> 00:06:58,900
Sa totoo lang.

47
00:07:31,940 --> 00:07:33,860
Your Grace, naghahanap ako ng audience.

48
00:07:35,380 --> 00:07:36,220
Pumasok.

49
00:07:42,300 --> 00:07:43,140
Yan,

50
00:07:44,300 --> 00:07:45,230
ano ang nagdadala sa iyo sa akin?

51
00:07:55,590 --> 00:07:56,430
Simu,

52
00:07:56,670 --> 00:07:58,230
Hindi maliit na bagay ang pagrerebelde ni Yan.

53
00:07:58,740 --> 00:08:00,500
Hindi niya magagawa

54
00:08:00,500 --> 00:08:01,550
nagawa ito ng mag-isa.

55
00:08:01,910 --> 00:08:03,110
Kahit na si Jiang Ai ay nagtrabaho sa amin

56
00:08:03,110 --> 00:08:04,500
sa pananambang kay Bai Sanxing,

57
00:08:04,860 --> 00:08:06,740
may kaugnayan pa rin siya kay Bai Sanxing.

58
00:08:07,230 --> 00:08:08,070
Bukod,

59
00:08:08,550 --> 00:08:09,910
may pakana ang kanyang Vice Lord laban sa iyo.

60
00:08:10,590 --> 00:08:12,110
Wala ba talaga siyang alam tungkol dito?

61
00:08:15,110 --> 00:08:16,380
Kung pinaghihinalaan mo si Jiang Ai,

62
00:08:17,300 --> 00:08:18,590
humanap ka ng patunay.

63
00:08:19,470 --> 00:08:20,910
Kung makakahanap ka ng patunay,

64
00:08:21,470 --> 00:08:22,990
Huhusgahan ko ito ng patas.

65
00:08:25,030 --> 00:08:25,990
Kawawa naman si Yan Zhang

66
00:08:25,990 --> 00:08:27,420
ay nakatagpo ng pagkalipol.

67
00:08:27,940 --> 00:08:28,780
Kung hindi,

68
00:08:28,990 --> 00:08:30,860
Marami pa sana akong natutunan.

69
00:08:31,300 --> 00:08:32,540
Apurahan ang sitwasyon noon.

70
00:08:32,780 --> 00:08:34,430
Sa pagmamadali ko, pinatay ko siya.

71
00:08:35,380 --> 00:08:36,220
ayos lang.

72
00:08:38,140 --> 00:08:39,140
Sa loob ng 300 taon,

73
00:08:40,110 --> 00:08:41,590
ang mga naghahangad na patayin ako

74
00:08:41,590 --> 00:08:42,470
naging marami.

75
00:08:42,780 --> 00:08:44,110
sanay na ako.

76
00:08:44,860 --> 00:08:45,900
Buti na lang nasa tabi ko

77
00:08:45,900 --> 00:08:46,900
kayo ba ni Jiang Ai.

78
00:08:47,430 --> 00:08:48,216
Kung hindi,

79
00:08:48,227 --> 00:08:49,807
hindi namin sila kinuha nang ganoon kadali.

80
00:08:51,710 --> 00:08:53,310
Salamat sa iyong maayos na pagpaplano, Simu.

81
00:08:53,860 --> 00:08:55,230
Sinunod ko lang ang plano.

82
00:09:05,190 --> 00:09:06,103
May isa pang bagay.

83
00:09:06,500 --> 00:09:08,590
Paano mo haharapin si Bai Sanxing?

84
00:09:10,670 --> 00:09:11,520
Kahit na ang Bilangguan

85
00:09:11,520 --> 00:09:13,190
hindi siya kayang sirain sa loob ng 300 taon.

86
00:09:14,310 --> 00:09:15,500
Nakahanap na ako ng ibang lugar

87
00:09:15,500 --> 00:09:16,470
para hawakan siya.

88
00:09:16,746 --> 00:09:17,782
Ngunit siya ay napukaw ng paghihimagsik

89
00:09:17,793 --> 00:09:18,660
paulit-ulit.

90
00:09:19,110 --> 00:09:20,350
Dapat natin siyang i-root out.

91
00:09:25,380 --> 00:09:27,140
Hindi mo na kailangang ipaalala sa akin iyon.

92
00:09:30,860 --> 00:09:32,310
Hindi pa naaayos ang kaguluhan.

93
00:09:33,020 --> 00:09:34,660
Si Jiang Ai ay lubhang nasaktan at nakaratay.

94
00:09:35,310 --> 00:09:37,260
Dapat marami kang dapat harapin.

95
00:09:37,990 --> 00:09:39,140
Asikasuhin mo muna.

96
00:09:48,190 --> 00:09:49,030
Oo.

97
00:10:28,140 --> 00:10:29,070
Your Grace,

98
00:10:29,070 --> 00:10:30,430
ang Kaliwang Kamay ay matatag na ngayon.

99
00:10:30,710 --> 00:10:31,976
Kailangan pa niya ng oras para makabawi.

100
00:10:36,780 --> 00:10:37,620
Ang iyong Grasya.

101
00:10:38,740 --> 00:10:39,580
kamusta ka na?

102
00:10:40,140 --> 00:10:42,020
Sinubukan ka ng Vice Lord ko na patayin.

103
00:10:42,470 --> 00:10:43,470
Nabigo akong makita ito

104
00:10:43,710 --> 00:10:44,660
at kontrolin siya.

105
00:10:45,260 --> 00:10:46,380
parusahan mo ako.

106
00:10:49,500 --> 00:10:50,340
Sa halip na iyon,

107
00:10:51,740 --> 00:10:52,830
Mas curious ako

108
00:10:53,900 --> 00:10:55,430
tungkol sa kung bakit mo iniligtas si Bai Sanxing.

109
00:11:06,310 --> 00:11:07,430
Noon, Bai Sanxing

110
00:11:08,230 --> 00:11:09,860
kinulong ako at kinokontrol

111
00:11:09,860 --> 00:11:10,900
tulad ng isang nakakulong na pag-aari.

112
00:11:11,780 --> 00:11:12,620
Hindi ako naging isa

113
00:11:12,620 --> 00:11:14,190
upang manipulahin.

114
00:11:15,020 --> 00:11:16,350
Kinaiinisan ko siya hanggang buto.

115
00:11:17,540 --> 00:11:18,710
Para sa 300 taon na ito,

116
00:11:18,710 --> 00:11:20,260
sa tuwing naiisip ko siya,

117
00:11:20,990 --> 00:11:22,470
Nais kong kaya ko

118
00:11:23,190 --> 00:11:24,380
tadtarin siya ng pira-piraso

119
00:11:24,620 --> 00:11:26,190
at tapos na sa kanya para sa kabutihan.

120
00:11:27,540 --> 00:11:28,990
Ngunit sa sandaling iyon,

121
00:11:31,620 --> 00:11:33,190
Hindi ako makatayo at panoorin siya

122
00:11:33,190 --> 00:11:34,140
mamatay sa harap ng aking mga mata.

123
00:11:36,620 --> 00:11:38,070
Sa loob-loob mo, nagmamalasakit ka pa rin sa kanya.

124
00:11:39,310 --> 00:11:40,590
Hindi mo lang aaminin.

125
00:11:46,380 --> 00:11:47,230
Huwag mo na itong pag-isipan.

126
00:11:48,540 --> 00:11:49,500
Nasaktan ka ng husto.

127
00:11:50,110 --> 00:11:50,950
Magpahinga ng maayos.

128
00:11:52,430 --> 00:11:53,270
Your Grace,

129
00:11:56,190 --> 00:11:57,030
paano

130
00:11:58,900 --> 00:12:00,070
siya na ba ngayon?

131
00:12:00,990 --> 00:12:01,830
Buhay pa.

132
00:12:32,860 --> 00:12:33,700
Grand Ancestor.

133
00:12:35,380 --> 00:12:36,950
Grand Ancestor, matagal nang hindi nagkikita.

134
00:12:37,110 --> 00:12:38,470
Akala ko nakalimutan mo na ako.

135
00:12:39,110 --> 00:12:39,990
Sa ilang araw,

136
00:12:41,070 --> 00:12:42,110
Pupunta ako sa Nandu.

137
00:12:42,380 --> 00:12:43,220
Grand Ancestor,

138
00:12:43,710 --> 00:12:44,990
pupunta ka sa Nandu?

139
00:12:52,580 --> 00:12:59,580
(Chamber of Buddha's Grace)

140
00:13:00,620 --> 00:13:01,470
Bibisita tayo

141
00:13:01,470 --> 00:13:02,310
nanay ko.

142
00:13:03,470 --> 00:13:04,380
Gusto niya itong tahimik.

143
00:13:20,020 --> 00:13:20,990
Sino ito?

144
00:13:24,950 --> 00:13:25,860
Xu.

145
00:13:30,470 --> 00:13:31,310
Nanay,

146
00:13:32,900 --> 00:13:33,740
nakabalik na ako.

147
00:13:35,900 --> 00:13:37,780
Nakakapagod ang paglalakbay mo kahapon.

148
00:13:38,540 --> 00:13:39,540
Ako lang...

149
00:13:43,020 --> 00:13:43,900
Umupo ka.

150
00:13:43,900 --> 00:13:44,780
Sige, maupo ka.

151
00:13:52,590 --> 00:13:53,620
Ito ay...

152
00:13:54,946 --> 00:13:56,209
Dinala ko siya sa battlefield

153
00:13:56,220 --> 00:13:56,790
bilang kapatid ko.

154
00:13:56,990 --> 00:13:57,830
Siya si Xue Chenying.

155
00:13:58,260 --> 00:13:59,140
Nawalan siya ng mga magulang.

156
00:13:59,900 --> 00:14:01,740
Ang kanyang kapatid na babae ay nakakuha ng mahusay na merito sa labanan.

157
00:14:02,470 --> 00:14:03,860
Nangako ako sa kanya na aalagaan ko siya.

158
00:14:04,900 --> 00:14:05,740
Chenying,

159
00:14:06,830 --> 00:14:07,670
bati ni Inay.

160
00:14:13,380 --> 00:14:14,260
Pagbati, Mrs. Duan.

161
00:14:16,260 --> 00:14:17,100
Bata,

162
00:14:17,740 --> 00:14:19,070
hindi na kailangan ng ganoong engrandeng bow.

163
00:14:19,830 --> 00:14:21,260
Na pumunta ka dito

164
00:14:21,260 --> 00:14:22,190
ay kapalaran sa sarili.

165
00:14:23,190 --> 00:14:24,143
Ang Buddha ay maawain.

166
00:14:24,660 --> 00:14:25,500
Ang lugar na ito

167
00:14:26,190 --> 00:14:27,470
magiging tahanan mo.

168
00:14:52,430 --> 00:14:54,230
Dito, magkaroon ng ilang mga pastry.

169
00:14:54,660 --> 00:14:55,500
salamat po.

170
00:15:01,230 --> 00:15:02,070
Chenying,

171
00:15:06,540 --> 00:15:07,380
sige, kumain ka na.

172
00:15:14,386 --> 00:15:15,540
Inay, sa tuwing nakikita mo ako,

173
00:15:15,540 --> 00:15:16,600
lagi kang reserved.

174
00:15:16,870 --> 00:15:18,039
Maaaring magsimulang maghinala si Jingyuan

175
00:15:18,050 --> 00:15:19,183
may alitan sa pagitan namin.

176
00:15:21,830 --> 00:15:22,990
Nararamdaman ko lang

177
00:15:23,740 --> 00:15:25,693
na sa lahat ng mga taon na ito,
Wala akong ginawa para sayo.

178
00:15:26,470 --> 00:15:28,430
Tutal, noong pinaka kailangan mo ako,

179
00:15:29,780 --> 00:15:31,190
Hindi ko kayang manatili sa tabi mo.

180
00:15:42,430 --> 00:15:43,370
Nag-o-overthink ka.

181
00:15:45,900 --> 00:15:46,740
Tungkol sa usaping ito,

182
00:15:48,590 --> 00:15:49,780
Kahit kailan hindi kita sinisi.

183
00:15:51,260 --> 00:15:53,470
Kaya naman

184
00:15:54,110 --> 00:15:55,660
Mas lalong sumama ang pakiramdam ko sa loob.

185
00:15:56,950 --> 00:15:58,110
Hindi kita kayang harapin.

186
00:16:07,380 --> 00:16:08,380
Marahil ang aking mga magulang

187
00:16:09,990 --> 00:16:10,990
nagkaroon ng isang bagay

188
00:16:11,860 --> 00:16:12,860
talagang hinanap nila.

189
00:16:15,260 --> 00:16:16,260
Kahit kadugo,

190
00:16:17,660 --> 00:16:18,660
sa kanilang mga mata,

191
00:16:19,900 --> 00:16:20,990
ang ibig sabihin ay napakaliit.

192
00:16:23,830 --> 00:16:24,950
Sa tingin ko ay hindi tama iyon,

193
00:16:26,430 --> 00:16:27,500
pero naiintindihan ko naman sila.

194
00:16:31,830 --> 00:16:32,710
Kung Xiaoxiao

195
00:16:32,710 --> 00:16:33,620
ay nandito ngayon.

196
00:16:36,900 --> 00:16:37,740
bakit naman

197
00:16:37,950 --> 00:16:40,110
Dahil tiyak na aaliwin ka niya,

198
00:16:40,500 --> 00:16:41,830
at pagaanin ang iyong kalungkutan.

199
00:16:53,310 --> 00:16:54,150
ayos lang.

200
00:16:54,740 --> 00:16:55,950
Hindi naman ako masyadong nabalisa.

201
00:16:56,740 --> 00:16:57,780
Pero umaasa pa rin ako sa kanya

202
00:16:58,500 --> 00:16:59,540
pumunta dito,

203
00:17:21,910 --> 00:17:22,750
Simu.

204
00:17:23,470 --> 00:17:25,060
Bakit kailangan nating pumunta dito?

205
00:19:20,670 --> 00:19:21,510
Simu,

206
00:19:23,663 --> 00:19:24,956
lumaki ka sa Mortal World.

207
00:19:25,460 --> 00:19:26,300
Palagi mong gusto

208
00:19:26,300 --> 00:19:27,580
mataong kasiglahan nito,

209
00:19:28,060 --> 00:19:29,633
sa halip na ang malamig na katahimikan ng Void.

210
00:19:31,710 --> 00:19:32,910
Kung gusto mo,

211
00:19:33,540 --> 00:19:34,540
magagawa natin ang Void

212
00:19:34,540 --> 00:19:35,820
matingkad at masigla

213
00:19:36,500 --> 00:19:37,470
tulad ng Mortal World.

214
00:19:39,780 --> 00:19:40,620
Yan,

215
00:19:41,780 --> 00:19:43,150
sinusubukan mo lang akong pasayahin.

216
00:19:44,797 --> 00:19:47,023
Ang walang laman ay nasa ilalim ng dagat,
walang liwanag ng araw.

217
00:19:47,260 --> 00:19:48,580
Paano ito magiging masigla?

218
00:19:50,150 --> 00:19:51,300
Kung gusto mo,

219
00:19:51,950 --> 00:19:53,230
Gagawin ko lahat ng makakaya ko

220
00:19:53,580 --> 00:19:54,420
para mangyari ito.

221
00:20:07,910 --> 00:20:08,750
Simu,

222
00:20:10,580 --> 00:20:11,820
May regalo ako sayo.

223
00:20:18,990 --> 00:20:19,830
Alam ko

224
00:20:20,540 --> 00:20:21,910
na hindi mo ginustong maging

225
00:20:23,300 --> 00:20:24,390
ang Soberano ng mga Espiritu,

226
00:20:24,390 --> 00:20:25,796
nakatali sa walang katapusang mga gawain ng Void.

227
00:20:26,990 --> 00:20:28,500
Babantayan ko ang Void para sa iyo.

228
00:20:30,100 --> 00:20:31,106
Ang mga naninindigan sa lahat

229
00:20:31,430 --> 00:20:32,390
madalas maglakad mag-isa.

230
00:20:33,190 --> 00:20:34,150
Ngunit mayroon ka sa akin.

231
00:20:34,740 --> 00:20:35,910
Lagi akong mananatili sa tabi mo.

232
00:20:40,100 --> 00:20:41,235
Tinalian ko na ang vital gate ko

233
00:20:41,246 --> 00:20:42,150
sa hairpin na ito.

234
00:20:43,430 --> 00:20:44,430
Ngayon, ibibigay ko sa iyo.

235
00:20:45,540 --> 00:20:46,820
Ito ang panata ng aking puso.

236
00:20:49,100 --> 00:20:50,020
Kung payag ka,

237
00:20:50,950 --> 00:20:52,580
Ako ay magiging iyo magpakailanman.

238
00:20:53,150 --> 00:20:54,076
Mamahalin kita magpakailanman,

239
00:20:54,710 --> 00:20:56,100
maging kaibigan mo,

240
00:20:56,540 --> 00:20:57,390
ang iyong kasintahan,

241
00:20:58,500 --> 00:20:59,430
at ang iyong Yan.

242
00:21:03,150 --> 00:21:03,990
Simu.

243
00:21:14,020 --> 00:21:15,260
Sorry, Yan.

244
00:21:16,300 --> 00:21:17,260
Hindi ko masasabing oo.

245
00:21:19,990 --> 00:21:21,430
Ikaw ang pinakapinagkakatiwalaan kong partner.

246
00:21:22,820 --> 00:21:23,660
Iyon lang.

247
00:21:29,910 --> 00:21:30,750
Simu, ikaw...

248
00:21:32,500 --> 00:21:33,990
Talaga bang tinatanggihan mo ako?

249
00:21:39,356 --> 00:21:40,352
Kung ayaw mo ngayon,

250
00:21:40,363 --> 00:21:41,140
ayos lang yan.

251
00:21:41,360 --> 00:21:42,230
Kaya kong itago ito para sa iyo.

252
00:21:42,230 --> 00:21:43,070
Yan,

253
00:21:44,300 --> 00:21:45,640
Halos gumaling na ang sugat ni Jiang Ai.

254
00:21:45,870 --> 00:21:46,990
Pwede na siyang ituloy ang duty bukas.

255
00:21:47,630 --> 00:21:48,992
Aalis ako sa pang-araw-araw na gawain ng Void

256
00:21:49,003 --> 00:21:49,540
sa inyong dalawa.

257
00:21:50,430 --> 00:21:51,540
Kailangan kong pumunta sa Nandu.

258
00:21:51,780 --> 00:21:52,620
Simu,

259
00:21:56,060 --> 00:21:57,020
Ayokong pumunta ka.

260
00:21:58,470 --> 00:22:00,470
Kung ano man yan, pupuntahan kita.

261
00:22:07,630 --> 00:22:08,470
Yan Ke,

262
00:22:15,230 --> 00:22:16,070
nalampasan mo na.

263
00:22:26,190 --> 00:22:27,030
Lumampas sa hakbang?

264
00:22:29,020 --> 00:22:31,150
Masyado akong mahigpit

265
00:22:31,382 --> 00:22:32,592
sa tamang code sa pagitan natin,

266
00:22:32,603 --> 00:22:33,420
kaya napabayaan mo ako.

267
00:22:33,420 --> 00:22:34,340
Kahit kailan hindi kita pinabayaan.

268
00:22:34,500 --> 00:22:36,020
Ikaw ang aking pinakapinagkakatiwalaang Kanang Kamay.

269
00:22:43,990 --> 00:22:44,950
Kapag wala ako,

270
00:22:45,820 --> 00:22:47,340
ang Void ay umaasa sa iyo at kay Jiang Ai.

271
00:22:48,500 --> 00:22:49,910
Kung tungkol sa sinabi mo kanina lang,

272
00:22:50,870 --> 00:22:52,260
Magpapanggap akong hindi ko narinig.

273
00:24:03,786 --> 00:24:04,852
Pagbati, Grand Ancestor.

274
00:24:08,190 --> 00:24:10,230
Grand Ancestor.

275
00:24:14,910 --> 00:24:15,950
Grand Ancestor.

276
00:24:25,990 --> 00:24:27,500
Para salubungin ako,

277
00:24:27,910 --> 00:24:29,430
nagbihis ka pa.

278
00:24:40,190 --> 00:24:41,150
Grand Ancestor,

279
00:24:43,020 --> 00:24:43,860
pwede bang

280
00:24:45,990 --> 00:24:47,820
isang beses lang makipagkamay?

281
00:24:52,390 --> 00:24:53,990
Para bang hindi tayo nagkita.

282
00:24:54,390 --> 00:24:55,470
Hindi na kailangang maging masyadong pormal.

283
00:24:57,540 --> 00:24:59,500
Iyon ay sa aking pagkabata.

284
00:25:00,150 --> 00:25:01,300
Naaalala ko lang

285
00:25:02,020 --> 00:25:04,020
hawak mo ako noon.

286
00:25:27,580 --> 00:25:29,150
Ganun pa rin ang nararamdaman.

287
00:25:56,910 --> 00:25:58,020
Bihira kang magkaroon ng pagkakataon

288
00:25:58,020 --> 00:25:58,950
upang pumunta sa Nandu.

289
00:25:59,190 --> 00:26:00,190
Gusto mo ba

290
00:26:00,340 --> 00:26:01,580
para tingnan si Duan Xu?

291
00:26:02,780 --> 00:26:03,630
wala akong oras.

292
00:26:04,230 --> 00:26:05,780
Si Heneral Duan ay hindi pa

293
00:26:05,910 --> 00:26:07,260
pagkakaroon ng madaling oras kamakailan lamang.

294
00:26:07,500 --> 00:26:08,950
Balita ko pinipili ng pamilya niya

295
00:26:08,950 --> 00:26:10,100
isang nobya para sa kanya sa mga araw na ito.

296
00:26:10,300 --> 00:26:11,470
Marahil bago magtagal,

297
00:26:11,470 --> 00:26:12,630
ikakasal na siya.

298
00:26:18,300 --> 00:26:19,190
Ano sa akin iyon?

299
00:26:27,950 --> 00:26:28,990
Grand Ancestor,

300
00:26:29,390 --> 00:26:30,580
kung tunay siyang mag-asawa,

301
00:26:30,710 --> 00:26:31,780
mawawala siya sayo.

302
00:26:31,780 --> 00:26:33,100
Hindi ba ito nalulungkot sa iyo?

303
00:26:33,670 --> 00:26:34,910
Si Duan Xu ay isang mortal.

304
00:26:35,530 --> 00:26:36,390
Pagsisimula ng isang pamilya

305
00:26:36,390 --> 00:26:37,820
ang pinaka natural na bagay para sa kanya.

306
00:26:39,390 --> 00:26:40,670
Bakit ako dapat malungkot?

307
00:26:41,060 --> 00:26:42,820
Hindi ba siya ang iyong spell bearer?

308
00:26:42,820 --> 00:26:44,190
Hindi ka ba nakakaawa?

309
00:26:46,300 --> 00:26:47,116
Kung payag pa siya

310
00:26:47,127 --> 00:26:48,230
para ipagpalit ang senses niya sa akin,

311
00:26:48,430 --> 00:26:49,670
ang arrangement namin

312
00:26:49,670 --> 00:26:50,820
magpapatuloy tulad ng dati.

313
00:26:51,950 --> 00:26:53,190
Ano ang dapat pagsisihan?

314
00:26:53,780 --> 00:26:55,030
- Ngunit...
- Sapat na.

315
00:26:55,630 --> 00:26:57,500
Dumating ako para sa mga seryosong bagay.

316
00:26:58,630 --> 00:27:00,020
Patawarin mo ako ng kalokohan.

317
00:27:05,340 --> 00:27:07,260
Last time, tinanong mo ako

318
00:27:07,390 --> 00:27:08,820
upang makagawa ng isang mahiwagang artifact.

319
00:27:09,020 --> 00:27:09,860
Ako ay...

320
00:27:10,020 --> 00:27:11,910
Huli na. Dapat matulog ka na.

321
00:27:14,230 --> 00:27:15,910
Nandito si Grand Ancestor ngayong gabi.

322
00:27:16,150 --> 00:27:17,430
May meeting kami.

323
00:27:18,707 --> 00:27:19,547
Iwanan ito bukas.

324
00:27:19,558 --> 00:27:21,642
(Ziji, katulong ni Hejia Fengyi)
Isinasaalang-alang ang iyong kalusugan,

325
00:27:21,652 --> 00:27:22,839
dapat tulog ka na.

326
00:27:26,540 --> 00:27:27,500
Ang iyong Grand Ancestor

327
00:27:28,820 --> 00:27:30,190
Nais ka rin ng mas mahabang buhay.

328
00:27:37,100 --> 00:27:37,940
ayos lang.

329
00:27:39,150 --> 00:27:40,060
Bukas na lang tayo mag-usap.

330
00:27:41,870 --> 00:27:43,230
Hindi mo ba gustong malaman

331
00:27:43,230 --> 00:27:44,950
sinong mga dalaga ang pinili ng angkan ni Duan?

332
00:27:44,950 --> 00:27:45,790
hindi ko.

333
00:28:04,670 --> 00:28:06,063
Your Grace, ako na ang mag-aayos ng pahinga mo.

334
00:28:06,230 --> 00:28:07,070
Sumama ka sa akin.

335
00:28:20,630 --> 00:28:22,740
Supot ng bango! Mga trinket!

336
00:28:23,150 --> 00:28:23,990
Xu,

337
00:28:24,580 --> 00:28:25,420
Hindi ko akalain

338
00:28:25,430 --> 00:28:26,770
ang mga babaeng pinili ni Ama para sa iyo

339
00:28:27,260 --> 00:28:28,100
ay napakaganda.

340
00:28:28,580 --> 00:28:30,580
Napakatalino mo.

341
00:28:31,230 --> 00:28:32,070
Paano ito?

342
00:28:32,300 --> 00:28:33,710
Mamasyal ka sa mga lansangan,

343
00:28:34,100 --> 00:28:35,190
naghahanap ng romansa.

344
00:28:35,390 --> 00:28:36,230
anong sabi mo

345
00:28:37,430 --> 00:28:38,300
Tumigil ka sa pagsasalita ng kalokohan.

346
00:28:39,190 --> 00:28:40,190
Paano na ang kalokohan?

347
00:28:40,950 --> 00:28:42,020
Fang Xianye

348
00:28:42,020 --> 00:28:43,390
magaling lang mag-aral.

349
00:28:43,580 --> 00:28:44,420
Ito ay walang espesyal.

350
00:28:44,870 --> 00:28:46,020
Ngunit maaari kang magsulat ng mga sanaysay

351
00:28:46,500 --> 00:28:48,540
upang patatagin ang kaharian

352
00:28:48,780 --> 00:28:51,060
at lumaban sa larangan ng digmaan.

353
00:28:52,060 --> 00:28:52,900
Paano ako

354
00:28:53,430 --> 00:28:54,270
humanap ng magandang laban

355
00:28:54,470 --> 00:28:55,670
para sayo ngayon?

356
00:28:55,670 --> 00:28:56,510
Ano sa tingin mo?

357
00:28:56,820 --> 00:28:58,500
Anong klaseng babae ang gusto mo?

358
00:29:03,500 --> 00:29:05,190
Gusto ko...

359
00:29:08,150 --> 00:29:09,230
Gusto ko

360
00:29:10,500 --> 00:29:11,780
isang babaeng hindi nahanap sa mundong ito.

361
00:29:15,710 --> 00:29:16,630
ayos lang.

362
00:29:16,630 --> 00:29:18,470
Pagkatapos ay pupunta ako upang mag-wish.

363
00:29:19,340 --> 00:29:20,780
I'll wish for Goddess Chang'e

364
00:29:21,150 --> 00:29:23,060
para bumaba at hanapin ka.

365
00:29:24,260 --> 00:29:25,100
Sige.

366
00:29:25,230 --> 00:29:26,190
Sa iyong tapat na puso,

367
00:29:26,740 --> 00:29:28,670
ang iyong panalangin ay maaaring magkatotoo.

368
00:29:29,390 --> 00:29:30,950
Xu, magseryoso ka ha?

369
00:29:32,300 --> 00:29:34,980
(Lotusborn Pavilion)

370
00:29:39,470 --> 00:29:40,310
Xu,

371
00:29:40,910 --> 00:29:42,630
hindi ka talaga sumama sa akin?

372
00:29:44,060 --> 00:29:44,900
Pumasok ka mag-isa.

373
00:29:47,740 --> 00:29:48,580
Sige na.

374
00:29:57,190 --> 00:29:58,500
Lahat, mangyaring maghintay ng ilang sandali.

375
00:29:58,710 --> 00:30:00,100
Malapit nang dumating ang Propeta

376
00:30:00,230 --> 00:30:02,260
para magsunog ng prayer paper para sa inyong lahat

377
00:30:02,260 --> 00:30:03,710
at magbigay ng mga pinagpalang bulaklak.

378
00:30:08,740 --> 00:30:09,580
Ito ay

379
00:30:11,430 --> 00:30:13,150
ang kandila ng kaluluwa mula sa Bilangguan.

380
00:30:13,820 --> 00:30:14,670
Grand Ancestor,

381
00:30:15,260 --> 00:30:16,910
naparito ka para sa bagay na ito?

382
00:30:17,740 --> 00:30:18,580
tama yan.

383
00:30:21,470 --> 00:30:22,950
Maaari bang ang mahiwagang artifact

384
00:30:24,100 --> 00:30:25,670
hiniling mo...

385
00:30:28,540 --> 00:30:29,630
300 taon na ang lumipas.

386
00:30:32,260 --> 00:30:34,260
Oras na para tapusin ito.

387
00:30:40,260 --> 00:30:41,466
Tanging ang mga nasa Mortal World

388
00:30:45,300 --> 00:30:46,430
maaaring maunawaan ang mga gawain nito.

389
00:30:52,260 --> 00:30:58,120
♪Ang mga naantig na alaala ay nananatili tulad ng mga anino♪

390
00:30:58,120 --> 00:31:02,580
(Lotusborn Pavilion)

391
00:31:04,850 --> 00:31:10,860
♪Kung pwede kitang tawaging ganito ng mahina♪

392
00:31:11,950 --> 00:31:16,000
♪Kasing banayad ng isang panandaliang yakap♪

393
00:31:16,020 --> 00:31:17,150
Kaya, ito ang tinatawag ng mga mortal

394
00:31:17,150 --> 00:31:18,163
ang abala ng mortal na buhay.

395
00:31:18,430 --> 00:31:19,710
Pinaghalong amoy talaga.

396
00:31:20,100 --> 00:31:21,100
Naaamoy ko lahat.

397
00:31:22,100 --> 00:31:22,940
Foxy,

398
00:31:23,430 --> 00:31:24,870
tikman mo lang ako.

399
00:31:24,880 --> 00:31:29,950
♪Ibinigay ang habambuhay
para maalala ang isang pangalan♪

400
00:31:30,480 --> 00:31:33,840
♪May mga hilig at sakit♪

401
00:31:34,040 --> 00:31:36,940
♪Sana maranasan natin silang magkasama♪

402
00:31:37,620 --> 00:31:42,310
♪Bago tayo makalimutan o maghiwalay♪

403
00:31:42,340 --> 00:31:43,180
Simu.

404
00:31:44,470 --> 00:31:45,310
Simu.

405
00:31:46,990 --> 00:31:47,830
anong ginagawa mo

406
00:31:47,920 --> 00:31:49,570
♪ Lumalabo at kumukupas♪

407
00:31:49,570 --> 00:31:51,320
♪Ano kaya ang mangyayari?♪

408
00:31:51,340 --> 00:31:52,180
Sorry

409
00:31:53,260 --> 00:31:54,100
sa kabastusan ko.

410
00:31:54,310 --> 00:31:55,960
♪Lalapit ako at tatakbo sa iyo♪

411
00:31:55,960 --> 00:31:59,140
♪Upang pagalingin ang pinakamalalim na sugat♪

412
00:31:59,660 --> 00:32:02,350
♪Mga himala, kawalang-hanggan, at ningning♪

413
00:32:02,350 --> 00:32:05,100
♪Mas mahalaga kaysa sa anumang tigang na lupa♪

414
00:32:05,200 --> 00:32:07,700
♪Maaari din ako
gugulin ang natitirang bahagi ng aking buhay♪

415
00:32:07,700 --> 00:32:11,670
♪Paglalakad kasama ka sa kawalang-hanggan♪

416
00:32:30,630 --> 00:32:31,780
Ang bango ng ulan.

417
00:32:33,060 --> 00:32:34,390
Dala ng ulan ang bango ng langit

418
00:32:35,230 --> 00:32:36,430
at inilalabas ang amoy ng lupa

419
00:32:37,540 --> 00:32:38,390
at ang sigla

420
00:32:38,390 --> 00:32:39,630
ng lahat ng bagay na may buhay.

421
00:32:40,690 --> 00:32:43,990
♪Tiisin ko ang nararamdaman mo♪

422
00:32:44,000 --> 00:32:44,930
Napakaganda.

423
00:32:45,310 --> 00:32:47,080
♪Mapalad akong nakilala kita♪

424
00:32:47,080 --> 00:32:49,720
♪Kung ganoon ay hindi kita bibitawan♪

425
00:32:50,060 --> 00:32:52,350
♪Sana maging firework ako♪

426
00:32:52,350 --> 00:32:56,670
♪Para masunog sa sandaling lumingon ka♪

427
00:33:24,081 --> 00:33:29,411
♪Sa pagitan ng itim at puti,
ripples crossed♪

428
00:33:29,741 --> 00:33:33,991
♪Light encountered shadow♪

429
00:33:35,351 --> 00:33:40,721
♪Natusok nito ang dilim at oras♪

430
00:33:41,021 --> 00:33:45,621
♪Ang hindi mababasag na kapalaran♪

431
00:33:46,711 --> 00:33:48,551
♪Biglang basag♪

432
00:34:00,761 --> 00:34:06,201
♪Sa pagitan ng itim at puti,
ripples crossed♪

433
00:34:06,381 --> 00:34:10,711
♪Light encountered shadow♪

434
00:34:12,081 --> 00:34:17,471
♪Natusok nito ang dilim at oras♪

435
00:34:17,701 --> 00:34:21,641
♪Ang hindi mababasag na kapalaran♪

436
00:34:23,411 --> 00:34:25,301
♪Biglang basag♪

437
00:34:27,961 --> 00:34:31,121
♪Makinig, umaatungal ang lahat ng tunog♪

438
00:34:31,121 --> 00:34:33,651
♪Habang ang malamig na yelo ay nagiging tides♪

439
00:34:33,651 --> 00:34:39,171
♪Ang kalungkutan ng isang siglo ay nakakatunaw ng mga pangarap♪

440
00:34:39,171 --> 00:34:42,411
♪Pagsunod sa patnubay ng tadhana♪

441
00:34:42,411 --> 00:34:47,271
♪Sa tadhana, ang ating mga sandali ay ipinagpalit♪

442
00:34:47,611 --> 00:34:50,631
♪Nagising ang puso bigla♪

443
00:34:50,631 --> 00:34:53,451
♪Panoorin ang pagbagsak ng mga paputok na parang bituin♪

444
00:34:53,711 --> 00:34:56,241
♪Ang bono na ito ay gusot sa isang thread♪

445
00:34:56,241 --> 00:35:01,661
♪Ang mga makamundong pagmuni-muni ay kumukupas sa ambon♪

446
00:35:01,831 --> 00:35:04,901
♪Pahiram ng isang panandaliang tibok ng puso♪

447
00:35:05,061 --> 00:35:09,961
♪Dinala mo ako sa mortal na alikabok,
hanggang sa nabighani ako sa mga alindog nito♪

448
00:35:10,171 --> 00:35:13,641
♪Ang puso ay nagising bigla♪

